Loading packages

library(leaflet)
## Warning: package 'leaflet' was built under R version 3.5.1
library(maps)
## Warning: package 'maps' was built under R version 3.5.1
France = map("france", fill = TRUE, plot = FALSE)
leaflet(data = France) %>% addTiles() %>%
  addPolygons(fillColor = topo.colors(10, alpha = NULL), stroke = FALSE)
